snippet.title: [PC] とばりんかー  ~ Tobarinker | Normal Mode + Endless Mode
snippet.description:
A cute little Hellsinker. fangame made by @tamajam on Twitter.

In this game, you control Tobari, while you protect Deadliar and Amber's fridge against an onslaught of Clammbons, Kaname Stones, Minogames, Fossil Maidens & Rusted Dragons. Grouped with bosses from the Shrine of Farewell.

Dont let bullets hit Deadliar, and dont let enemies reach the fridge, a simple game but very fun!
